      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784203112511,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirements\n- Users should be able to click the ad and be redirected to target\n- Advertisers can query ad click metric over time at 1Min interval\n\nNon-Functional Requirements\n- Scalable to support 10K clicks per second\n- Low latency analytics queries < 1s\n- Idempotency of ad clicks\n- Fault tolerance\n- Data integrity\n- As realtime as possible\n- \n\nScale \n- 10M ads at any given time\n- 10K add clicks per second at peak",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirements\n- Users should be able to click the ad and be redirected to target\n- Advertisers can query ad click metric over time at 1Min interval\n\nNon-Functional Requirements\n- Scalable to support 10K clicks per second\n- Low latency analytics queries < 1s\n- Idempotency of ad clicks\n- Fault tolerance\n- Data integrity\n- As realtime as possible\n- \n\nScale \n- 10M ads at any given time\n- 10K add clicks per second at peak",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "le3BDTQPcfnXcrznJnR4x",
