      "version": 474,
      "versionNonce": 885640121,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784207878112,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Streaming Solution:",
      "fontSize": 27.601902173913057,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Streaming Solution:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
    {
      "id": "AkVeAuq-m5KoskMgnP-q_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1115.98046875,
      "y": 1918.02734375,
      "width": 902.63916015625,
      "height": 120,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1F",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 228858135,
      "version": 602,
      "versionNonce": 1589187191,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784206531468,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- The ad click is sent to click Processor service\n- the click processor writes the click event to Database(Cassandra).\n- Aevery N min cron scheduler runs then Spark reads all clicks for that N window (Lets say N =1Min e.g., 9:01–9:02).\n- Spark aggregates the data (e.g., Ad-1 = 542 clicks).\n- The aggregated results are written to an OLAP database (ClickHouse/Druid) for fast dashboard queries.\n- Advertisers can query the OLAP database to get metrics on their ads.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- The ad click is sent to click Processor service\n- the click processor writes the click event to Database(Cassandra).\n- Aevery N min cron scheduler runs then Spark reads all clicks for that N window (Lets say N =1Min e.g., 9:01–9:02).\n- Spark aggregates the data (e.g., Ad-1 = 542 clicks).\n- The aggregated results are written to an OLAP database (ClickHouse/Druid) for fast dashboard queries.\n- Advertisers can query the OLAP database to get metrics on their ads.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
