      "index": "b1d",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1594848887,
      "version": 73,
      "versionNonce": 1912775863,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784207761477,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "That delay may be acceptable sometimes, but not for real-time dashboards",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "That delay may be acceptable sometimes, but not for real-time dashboards",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bAHbzfItt3NIc5gvw_Xc-",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1100.30078125,
      "y": 2845.2421875,
      "width": 590.3355102539062,
      "height": 120,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1e",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 629396407,
      "version": 397,
      "versionNonce": 1081515449,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784208238786,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Instead of waiting 1Min... process every click immediately\nwhen Click happens(user click ad-1) immediately send it to kafka\nThese events arrive Continuously.\nFlink reads the events, flink doesn't wait. Every click is processed instantly\n\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Instead of waiting 1Min... process every click immediately\nwhen Click happens(user click ad-1) immediately send it to kafka\nThese events arrive Continuously.\nFlink reads the events, flink doesn't wait. Every click is processed instantly\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "nDE0QqziOEZuPiuHqB_RH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1079.9140625,
      "y": 2966.765625,
      "width": 693.2632446289062,
      "height": 360,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1g",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1616145911,
      "version": 232,
      "versionNonce": 758686455,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784208511329,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Events arrive\n    - 9:01:10 Ad-1\n          Ad-1 Count = 1\n    - 9:01:12 Ad-1\n           Ad-1 Count = 2\n    - 9:01:20 Ad-2\n           Ad-1 Count = 2 \n           Ad-2 Count = 1\nFlink simply keeps increment the count\n\nInternally\n\nMinute 9:01\nAd-1 -> 2\nAd-2 -> 1\n\nThis state lives in RAM(memory) because reading and updating memory is extremely fast.\n  (and is backed by checkpoints for fault tolerance).",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Events arrive\n    - 9:01:10 Ad-1\n          Ad-1 Count = 1\n    - 9:01:12 Ad-1\n           Ad-1 Count = 2\n    - 9:01:20 Ad-2\n           Ad-1 Count = 2 \n           Ad-2 Count = 1\nFlink simply keeps increment the count\n\nInternally\n\nMinute 9:01\nAd-1 -> 2\nAd-2 -> 1\n\nThis state lives in RAM(memory) because reading and updating memory is extremely fast.\n  (and is backed by checkpoints for fault tolerance).",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
