      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784208552781,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "What happens if Flink crashes?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "What happens if Flink crashes?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
    {
      "id": "noux6CndZfPnA4BaZxezw",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1066.328125,
      "y": 3386.84375,
      "width": 310.2397155761719,
      "height": 300,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1l",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 841394809,
      "version": 67,
      "versionNonce": 944272313,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784208627327,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Ad-1 = 2\nAd-2 = 1\n\n💥 Server crashes\n\nEverything in RAM disappears\n\nWhen Flink restarts, it would think:\n\nAd-1 = 0\nAd-2 = 0\n\nNow the previous clicks are lost.\n\nThat would produce incorrect analytics.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Ad-1 = 2\nAd-2 = 1\n\n💥 Server crashes\n\nEverything in RAM disappears\n\nWhen Flink restarts, it would think:\n\nAd-1 = 0\nAd-2 = 0\n\nNow the previous clicks are lost.\n\nThat would produce incorrect analytics.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "YzQM5VXCUIHo8oP7VWPcA",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1059.51171875,
      "y": 3701.01640625,
      "width": 104.25990295410156,
      "height": 23,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1m",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1722286681,
      "version": 43,
      "versionNonce": 250162873,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784210548947,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Checkpoints",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Checkpoints",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
    {
      "id": "ScPJr1-vPz8UX_mmlT_rx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1039.0389099121094,
      "y": 3733.5734375,
      "width": 862.0952758789062,
      "height": 220,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1n",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 42539449,
      "version": 305,
      "versionNonce": 1965483127,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784210558068,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- To avoid losing state, Flink periodically saves a snapshot of its current state.\n       \n Checkpoint #1\n            Ad-1 = 120\n            Ad-2 = 48\n            Ad-3 = 89\n\n- This snapshot is written to durable storage (for example, S3, HDFS, or another persistent storage system).\n- When Flink restarts, it loads the last checkpoint.\n- Then it continues processing the remaining events from Kafka.\n- The events between the checkpoint and the crash are replayed.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- To avoid losing state, Flink periodically saves a snapshot of its current state.\n       \n Checkpoint #1\n            Ad-1 = 120\n            Ad-2 = 48\n            Ad-3 = 89\n\n- This snapshot is written to durable storage (for example, S3, HDFS, or another persistent storage system).\n- When Flink restarts, it loads the last checkpoint.\n- Then it continues processing the remaining events from Kafka.\n- The events between the checkpoint and the crash are replayed.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-PoymcXkVfU-F8fZIZSmD",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1035,
      "y": 3974.7,
      "width": 72.13995361328125,
      "height": 23,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
