      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Example of Late Events:\n    - Suppose someone clicked at \n        9:01:50\n\n    - But because of network delay...\n    - Kafka receives it at \n        9:02:10\n\n    - If your consumer uses processing time\n    - It thinks\n        Current time = 9:02\n        Put it into 9:02 bucket.\n    - Wrong.❌\n\n    - The click actually happened at\n         9:01:50\n\n    - It belongs in the 9:01 window.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Example of Late Events:\n    - Suppose someone clicked at \n        9:01:50\n\n    - But because of network delay...\n    - Kafka receives it at \n        9:02:10\n\n    - If your consumer uses processing time\n    - It thinks\n        Current time = 9:02\n        Put it into 9:02 bucket.\n    - Wrong.❌\n\n    - The click actually happened at\n         9:01:50\n\n    - It belongs in the 9:01 window.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
