      "index": "b2Y",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 894712119,
      "version": 11,
      "versionNonce": 2041162809,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1784211961380,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Now, when a click comes in:\n- The click processor service writes the event to a stream like Kafka or Kinesis.\n- A stream processor like Flink or Spark Streaming reads the events from the stream and aggregates them in real-time.\n- The aggregated data is stored in our OLAP database for querying.\n- Advertisers can query the OLAP database to get metrics on their ads in near real-time.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Now, when a click comes in:\n- The click processor service writes the event to a stream like Kafka or Kinesis.\n- A stream processor like Flink or Spark Streaming reads the events from the stream and aggregates them in real-time.\n- The aggregated data is stored in our OLAP database for querying.\n- Advertisers can query the OLAP database to get metrics on their ads in near real-time.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
